  return fromEntries(Object.keys(rules).map((key) => [`react/${key}`, 2]));
}

const activeRulesConfig = configureAsError(activeRules);

        'react/no-string-refs': 2,
        'react/no-unescaped-entities': 2,

        'react/prop-types': 2,
        'react/react-in-jsx-scope': 2,

        },

    },
    'jsx-runtime': {

      ],

        },
